               <code>
                  <coding>
                     <system value="http://loinc.org"/>
                     <code value="8648-8"/>
                     <display value="Hospital Course"/>
                  </coding>
               </code>
               <text>
                  <status value="generated"/>
                  <div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">Dear colleague, thank you for referring this 61-year-old male patient, admitted on 04.06.2024 due to substance dependence. On admission, a comprehensive psychiatric and somatic assessment confirmed polysubstance dependence (ICD-10: F19.2), with clinical features consistent with dependence syndrome affecting multiple substances. Withdrawal monitoring was initiated immediately. During the inpatient stay, structured detoxification was performed under close medical supervision, including pharmacological withdrawal management and stabilisation measures. Psychoeducational counselling was provided, and motivational intervention was conducted to support engagement with subsequent addiction treatment. The patient was discharged on 06.06.2024 in a stabilised condition. We strongly recommend continued outpatient addiction counselling and referral to a structured rehabilitation programme. Should signs of relapse or withdrawal recur, prompt re-evaluation is advised. Please do not hesitate to contact us with any queries.</div>
               </text>
            </section>
